# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

Only the latest version of this app is supported with security updates.

| Version | Supported |
| ------- | --------- |
| Latest  | ✅ Yes    |
| Older  | ❌ No     |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security vulnerability, please report it responsibly.

### How to report
- Email: **contact@inplay-tech.com**
- Subject: **Security Issue – NanoBeacon Sensor App**

Please include:
- A clear description of the issue
- Steps to reproduce (if applicable)
- Screenshots or logs (if helpful)

### What to expect
- I will acknowledge your report as soon as possible
- I will investigate and fix confirmed issues in a future update
- Please do **not** publicly disclose vulnerabilities before a fix is released

Thank you for helping keep this project secure.
